quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,32,"O daali: "eey ma ibliisa, e ko he…ď maa a laatodaaki e sujju…ďe …ďeen?""
  15,33,"O wi'i: "mi wonatah sujjanoowo …ďanndinke mo tagu…óaa immorde e sen∆īayngal, e loopal-…ďalewal …ďowrungal"."
  15,34,"O daali: "Yaltu toon, aan o ko a diiwaa…óo,"
  15,35,"pellet, kuddi fawike e ma haa √Īande njo…ďdi diina"."
  15,36,"O wi'i : "joomi am, nee…ďnitanam haa √Īande nde…ďe immintintee"."
  15,37,"O daali:"Aa,ko a jeyaa…óo e nee…ďnitantee…ďe …ďen."
  15,38,"haa e √Īalaande happu ganndaa…óo"."
  15,39,"O wi'i: "Joomi am, sabu ko mbewnu…óaa mi kon, ma mi cu…óinan …ďe ka leydi, ma mi bewnu …ďe fow ma…ď…ďe,"
  15,40,"si wanaa jeyaa…ďe maa, la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe"."
  15,41,"O daali: "nogol …óoo ko laawol ka am poocciingol."
  15,42,"Pellet, jeyaa…ďe am …ďen, a alanaa …ďe cemmbe, si wonaa …ďeen bew…ďe jokku…ďe ma."
  15,43,"Pellet Jahannama on wonii fodoore ma…ď…ďe …ďe fof."
  15,44,"Henge mari dame jee…ói…ói; damal kala e majje no mari ge…óal senndaangal."
  15,45,"Pellet, gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen wonii e aljannaaji e …ďulli."
  15,46,""Naatiree …ói e kisial, ko on hoolii…ďe"."
  15,47,"Min …óoofi kala ko woni e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe e konnaagu(cokotaagal): …ďe ngonti musi…ó…ďe fewtondir…ďe e dan…óe."
  15,48,"Tampere he…ďataa …ďe toon,, …ďe ngonah kadi yaltintee …ďe toon."
  15,49,"Yeetito jeyaa…ďe am …ďen, ko miin woni jaafotoo…óo, jurmtoo…óo On"
  15,50,"e wonnde lepte am …óeen, ko …óen ngoni lepte muus…óe …óen."
  15,51,"ha…ďru …ďe kadi fii ho…ď…ďe Ibraahiima …ďeen,"